1. *Poslušaj* me pažljivo. (Listen to me carefully.)
2. Ja sam te *poslušao* i uradio sam onako kako si mi rekao. (I listened to you and did as you told me.)
3. Da li si ti *poslušala* moj savet? (Did you listen to my advice?)
4. Oni su bili vrlo uporni i nisu hteli da *poslušaju* naše zahteve. (They were very persistent and didn't want to listen to our demands.)
5. Kada budeš spreman da me *poslušaš*, ja ću ti reći šta je potrebno da uradiš. (When you're ready to listen to me, I'll tell you what you need to do.)
6. *Poslušajte* molim vas, ovu pesmu. (Please listen to this song.)
7. Ako mi ne budeš *poslušao*, biće posledica. (If you don't listen to me, there will be consequences.)
8. *Poslušajmo* savet starijih kolega, oni znaju šta rade. (Let's listen to the advice of our older colleagues, they know what they're doing.)
9. Molim vas da mi *poslušate* objašnjenje. (Please listen to my explanation.)
10. Nisam siguran da li si dobro *poslušao* ono što sam ti rekao. (I'm not sure if you listened carefully to what I told you.)